Package edu.ncsu.csc316.cleaning.manager

Class CleaningManager

java.lang.Object
edu.ncsu.csc316.cleaning.manager.CleaningManager
public class CleaningManager extends Object
CleaningManager deals with functionality of getting a collection of cleaning events by room and calculating the area coverage of the vacuum after a specific time. An instance of this class is used in ReportManager. For fields, CleaningManager has a List of RoomRecord objects, a List of CleaningLogEntry objects, and a Map of entries storing Strings and RoomRecords.
Author:
Benjamin Uy
